lam\nproperty with respect to $\\\\tau$ if and only if the given homotopy class lifts\nto the torus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2016 12:04:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-02"}
